name: Arthemy Comics
description:
✦ Comics Arthemy - Quick Start ✦

1_____ I highly suggest to use these embeddings:

  • easynegative https://civitai.com/models/7808/easynegative

  • bad-hands-5 https://huggingface.co/yesyeahvh/bad-hands-5/tree/main

  • verybadimagenegative_v1.3 https://civitai.com/models/11772/verybadimagenegativehttps://civitai.com/models/11772/verybadimagenegative

2_____Size: Around 640 x 768

3_____Prompt: Start from the prompt of the pictures I've uploaded and then customize the areas focused on Character, Setting, Emotions, Colors and Aesthetic.

  • Quick Prompt:

    (artwork:1.2),(lineart:1.33),[CHARACTER | SETTING | EMOTIONS],(hyperdefined),(inked-art),[COLORS | AESTHETIC],complex lighting,(flat colors),ultradetailed,(fine-details:1.2),absurdres,(atmosphere)

  • Quick Negative Prompt:

    easynegative,bad-hands-5, verybadimagenegative_v1.3, (sketch),lowres,(text,words:1.3),watermark,(simple background),glitch,(jpeg-artifact:1.2), desaturated, compressed

4_____Upscale: to get crisp results like the one shown in the pictures use HiResFix and Real-ESRGAN. I suggest to use this step only on the preferred pictures, since it's quite heavy on the performance side.

I hope you like my merge and I can't wait to see what you all are going to create with it!

For future update, about the AI Editor I'm building with an italian team and my models you can check:

https://www.instagram.com/arthemy_vision/


____________________________________

If you like Comics Vision, remember to check these other models and consider to support their creators!

modelVersions.name: v4.0
modelVersions.description:
An updated mix with improved "Comic" Style.

For the fans of my previous models: I'm soon going to release a more general "Fantasy" model soon - stay tuned!

Since this model has been merged with the "Merge Block Weighted" function it is even more asymmetric - you'll notice the image changing a lot in the first and the last steps of the generation due to this.
